402
00:27:01.061 --> 00:27:03.187
MAN: <i>Good afternoon.
my fellow clergymen.</i>

403
00:27:03.322 --> 00:27:05.261
<i>I am Father Marcus Littleton.</i>

404
00:27:05.397 --> 00:27:08.461
