<i>myriad writings and glyphs.</i>

430
00:28:29.943 --> 00:28:33.748
<i>Its pages contain ancient
rituals and incantations.</i>

431
00:28:33.884 --> 00:28:35.582
<i>the recitation of which</i>

432
00:28:35.717 --> 00:28:38.288
<i>proclaim to allow contact
with supernatural forces</i>

433
00:28:38.424 --> 00:28:41.794
<i>that exist beyond the thin
veneer of our known world.</i>

434
